  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of the study is to assess in a prospective series of patients with high tumor
      burden follicular lymphoma treated with R-CHOP, the predictive value of [18F]-FDG PET
      performed over (after 4 treatments), and at the end of the first-line treatment on
      progression-free survival at 2 years.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
